<div class = "container-fluid" >
  <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4 col-lg-3">
    <div class="panel panel-default">
      <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="headingOne">
        <h5 class="panel-title text-center purpletext">Status</h5>
      </div>
      <div class="panel-body text-center">
        <% case card[:validation_status] when 0 %><h5>No Expert Check</h5>
          <% when 1 %><h5>Submitted for Expert Check</h5>
          <% when 2 %><h5>Validated Expert Check</h5>
          <% else %><h5>Status Unknown</h5>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>  
    <div class="spacebox30 col-xs-12"></div>      
  </div>   
  <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-8 col-lg-9 purpletext">
    <p>
      Having an Expert validation of your cards does not fully guarantee they are genuine, but adds a layer of trust and protection of your assets. <br><br>
      When you Submit a card for Expert Check, you deactivate other possible actions such as transfer or editiing, until the Expert has checked the card or until you cancel the submission. <br><br>
      Once a card is submitted, go see an Expert and give him your e-mail address, he should be able to see the cards you submitted and compare their digital identity with their physical one. <br><br>
    </p>
    <div class="col-xs-8 col-xs-offset-2 col-md-4 col-md-offset-4 col-lg-4 col-lg-offset-4">
      <a href="/experts" type="button" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary btn-purple btn-block">Expert List</a>
    </div> 
  </div>  
  <div class="spacebox30 col-xs-12"></div> 
  <% if card[:transfer_status] == 0 and (card[:owner_id] == current_user[:_id]) %>
    <div class="col-xs-12">  
      <% case card[:validation_status] when 0 %>
          <div class="col-xs-8 col-xs-offset-2 col-md-4 col-md-offset-4 col-lg-4 col-lg-offset-4">
            <a href="#{cards_validation_get_url_path(card)}" type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-purple btn-block btn-lg">Submit</a>
          </div>
        <% when 1 %>
          <div class="col-xs-8 col-xs-offset-2 col-md-4 col-md-offset-4 col-lg-4 col-lg-offset-4">
            <a href="#{cards_validation_cancel_url_path(card)}" type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-purple btn-block btn-lg">Cancel</a>
          </div>
        <% when 2 %>
          <div class="col-xs-8 col-xs-offset-2 col-md-4 col-md-offset-4 col-lg-4 col-lg-offset-4">
            <a href="#{cards_validation_get_url_path(card)}" type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-purple btn-block btn-lg">Submit Again</a>
          </div>
        <% else %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</div>      






